intro:
# Project kickoff

A few quick questions to set up your workspace. Here's the shape of what we're configuring:

- **Workspace** — name and primary language
- **Integrations** — what to wire up on day one
- **Priority** — how urgent this is

```mermaid
flowchart LR
  A[Kickoff] --> B[Configure]
  B --> C[Build]
  C --> D[Ship]
```

The generated config will look roughly like:

```ts
type Workspace = {
  name: string;
  language: "TypeScript" | "Go" | "Rust" | "Python";
  integrations: string[];
};
```
